Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.00,0:22:55.00,ed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H05F4F5&\3c&H003845&\bord1.8}如果有人说那是奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.00,0:22:55.00,ed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H05F4F5&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord4}如果有人说那是奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.00,0:23:00.46,ed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0500FB&\3c&HFFFFFF&}和你紧紧相连的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.05,0:23:05.59,ed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H64CB00&\3c&HFFFFFF&}除了“心灵感应”还能是什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.80,0:23:08.26,ed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFB4EF8&\3c&HFFFFFF&}啦啦啦 再再再 再发现！
